ing: 1 cup sweet onion, cut into wedges
1 papaya - peeled, seeded, and cut into wedges
1/4 cup three cheese Italian salad dressing
des: "Tomatoes, sweet onions, and papaya are tossed with a zesty, cheesy dressing. This quick and easy salad will not only be attractive to your eyes, but also your mouth!"
ins: In a bowl, mix the tomatoes, onion, and papaya. Pour in the dressing, and toss to coat.
